Description.value:
This iFlow replicates customers addresses from SAP ERP to YaaS using the ADRMAS iDoc. The address independent iDocs will be currently ignored. 
If the YaaS address is not existing, it will be created. 
If the YaaS address exists, the data will be updated. The update will be done only if the attributes are different and an update is needed.
If the YaaS customer is not existing, a blank customer with the ERP customer number will be created. 

Besides of the main address attributes also the entire iDoc is stored in the iDoc_ADRMAS mixin. In this way also ERP specific fields are stored on the YaaS address object. 
The iFlow also updates the e-mail address on the YaaS customer level. 
Deletion of the YaaS addresses is not presupposed, since address is a mandatory field for customers.
